#Retinoblastoma is an #EyeCancer that begins in the retina @EyeCancerr @Retino_blastoma @Retinoblastomaa
Your retina is made up of nerve tissue that senses light as it comes through the front of your eye #Retinoblastoma
The retina sends signals through your optic nerve to your brain, where these signals are interpreted as images. #Retinoblastoma
A rare form of #EyeCancer, #retinoblastoma is the most common form of cancer affecting the eye in children http://t.co/zS0mynPtRU
#Retinoblastoma may occur in one or both eyes. http://t.co/zS0mynPtRU
A white color in the center circle of the eye (pupil) when light is shone in the eye, such as when taking a flash photograph #retinoblastoma
Eyes that appear to be looking in different directions #retinoblastoma #symptoms http://t.co/zmNXiXjWjS
>Eye redness >Eye swelling #Retinoblastoma #symptoms http://t.co/zmNXiXjWjS
#Retinoblastoma occurs when nerve cells in the retina develop genetic mutations @EyeCancerr @RosemaryEyecare @Retinoblastomaa
#Retinoblastoma can also spread to other areas of the body, including the brain and spine. http://t.co/Gb04lkQHxH
it's possible for children to inherit a genetic mutation from their parents. #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/Gb04lkQHxH
Gene mutations that increase the risk of #retinoblastoma and other cancers can be passed from parents to children http://t.co/Gb04lkQHxH
Children treated for #retinoblastoma have a risk of cancer returning in and around the treated eye http://t.co/qAwHPrsgp9

Your eye doctor will conduct an eye exam to determine what's causing your child's signs and symptoms. #Retinoblastoma
Scans, imaging tests can help your child's doctor determine whether #Retinoblastoma has grown to affect other structures around the eye
Imaging tests may include ultrasound, computerized tomography (CT) scan and magnetic resonance imaging (MRI), among others #Retinoblastoma
Chemotherapy is a drug treatment that uses chemicals to kill cancer cells #Retinoblastoma
Chemotherapy may be used to treat #retinoblastoma that has spread to tissues outside the eyeball or to other areas of the body
Radiation therapy uses high-energy beams, such as X-rays, to kill cancer cells #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
During internal radiation, the treatment device is temporarily placed in or near the tumor. #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
Internal radiation for #retinoblastoma uses a small disk made of radioactive material. http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
The disk is stitched in place and left for a few days while it slowly gives off radiation to the tumor #Retinoblastoma
Placing radiation near the tumor reduces the chance that treatment will affect healthy eye tissue. #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
External beam radiation delivers high-powered beams to the tumor from a large machine outside of the body #Retinoblastoma
During laser therapy, a laser is used to destroy blood vessels that supply oxygen and nutrients to the tumor #Retinoblastoma @EyeCancerr
Cryotherapy uses extreme cold to kill cancer cells #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
During cryotherapy, a very cold substance, such as liquid nitrogen, is placed in or near the cancer cells #Retinoblastoma
Thermotherapy uses extreme heat to kill cancer cells. #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
During thermotherapy, heat is directed at the cancer cells using ultrasound, microwaves or lasers. #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
When the tumor is too large to be treated by other methods, surgery may be used to treat #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
Surgery to remove the eye may help prevent the spread of cancer to other parts of the body #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
During surgery to remove the eye, surgeons disconnect the muscles and tissue around the eye and remove the eyeball #Retinoblastoma
Surgery to place an eye implant #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
The muscles that control eye movement are attached to the implant #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
The eye muscles will adapt to the implanted eyeball, so it may move just as the natural eye #Retinoblastoma http://t.co/AdFvscMTx3
